rmal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n貢串<br />\n龍船<br />\n全記茶記<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n經濟d 既話<br />\n一麵之緣<br />\n街市高記 雙餸飯23 加汽水<br />\n西貢冰室<br />\n雪糕佬<br />\n<br />\n日本野既話 真係麻麻<br />\n食takka 不如食cowboy lunch 有魚生飯加野<span style=\"color: red;\">飲</span>45-55</blockquote>"},{"pid":"a995af8f7712f74d39c9998066336649fcfbe555","tid":380751,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T14:48:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Takka我覺得午餐算ok,不過夜晚真係唔抵食,同埋啲侍應個樣好無神 黑口黑面咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n直情弱智啦<br />\n有次食飯我後到，屋企人叫左支大吟釀座熱飲，我一睇就知出事，常識黎講大部分大吟釀都唔太啱熱飲<br />\n我 : 咦，熱飲喎<br />\n屋企人: 係呀，嗰位呀哥介紹架<br />\n樓面: 係呀，依枝酒最啱熱飲乜乜乜下省一百字<br />\n我擰轉個樽，後面標籤熱飲個欄大大個交叉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"565e8ae379cdf88c38a614d120c65ee90bfe8ad6","tid":380751,"uid":9502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T14:56:43.000Z","msg":"仲未有人講碗仔翅魚肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"129170ffd0d4ddb6e3ff1c774eec2dd9c8b2669c","tid":380751,"uid":44747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T16:00:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Takka我覺得午餐算ok,不過夜晚真係唔抵食,同埋啲侍應個樣好無神 黑口黑面咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n直情弱智啦<br />\n有次食飯我後到，屋企人叫左支大吟釀座熱飲，我一睇就知出事，常識黎講大部分大吟釀都唔太啱熱飲<br />\n我 : 咦，熱飲喎<br />\n屋企人: 係呀，嗰位呀哥介紹架<br />\n樓面: 係呀，依枝酒最啱熱飲乜乜乜下省一百字<br />\n我擰轉個樽，後面標籤熱飲個欄大大個交叉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得佢未